The paper deals with texture retrieval, which is a common problem in computer vision and falls under the category of computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Texel-Att, a texel-based descriptor, suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-category of multimedia (cs.MM). The paper also involves retrieval from a large repository, which suggests that it may fall under the sub-category of information retrieval (cs.IR). The use of distance functions for ranking suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-category of machine learning (cs.LG). Finally, the use of Texel-Att, a recent descriptor, suggests that the paper may also fall under the sub-category of artificial intelligence (cs.AI).
